QuestData.Title: The Wavespeaker
QuestData.Description: One of the Earthen Ring, Wavespeaker Valoren, swam down into the Nightmare Depths to the northeast. We haven't heard from her in awhile.$B$BSwim out there and see if you can find her.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find Wavespeaker Valoren in the Nightmare Depths of Vashj'ir.
